Quickstrike:



Quickstrike glared swiftly to Black Arachnia. He had nearly forgotten 
about that. She was right. It did make him nervous. "Yeah," he said 
to her. "Ah am, t' uh point. But ah guess we's could use another 
bot 'round here." He lightly tilted his head. "But ya know, ya can 
always delete it. Yer choice, though. Yer decision's mah decision." 
He never guessed there would be something that would come on-line 
with his genes. It was bizzare. He tried to hide it that he was 
truely nervous about the whole thing.
